imdb.plot outline: "Freshman Senator" What happens to the freshman senator on his first day when everyone from the lobbyist to the call girl on Capitol Hill hit on him. "Guess Who's Coming to Dinner?" A spoof on the original film where Michelle Obama invites the Palins for dinner. "Skamwell" An ad for cleaning out your secret files without leaving a trace. "Bail to the Chief" While President Obama explains his new budget plans, the the reporters and Oprah Winfrey upstage him. "Woop!" A theater of the absurd rendition of a businessman who bumps into another businessman while walking to work on the grounds of the National Mall.
